channel.description:
[center]This is a project to recreate DeltaScape on a cleaner and much more efficient base. We will also be changing a few things around but not pushing it to much.

Mod Jay (RooneyScape) Mod Dylan (Dust r i p)
[b]Update Log[/b] [code][07/05/2013] Mining Added! [06/05/2013] Woodcutting Added! [06/07/2013] Orb teleportations system added! [06/07/2013] Basic Music system added! [06/08/2013] Basic Sound system added! [06/11/2013] Custom objects located on entrana have been added! [06/12/2013] The Explosive potion added with a far more advanced twist! [06/12/2013] Bank Pin system added! [06/14/2013] Slayer added! [06/15/2013] RSMV items added! [06/16/2013] Combat finished! (including pvm!) [06/16/2013] Started on bosses![/code]

item.title: ThetaScape, Re-Creating THE private server with the technology we own today!
item.dc:creator: @rooneyscape rooneyscape
item.description:
@rooneyscape wrote:

[quote=“Uncalled, post:4, topic:521554”]I like the development so far. I suggest that you use your thread better, and make it more detailed. Add information regarding the server, what your plans are, if you’re going to be hosting, etc. Just add in filler information and try to kill as many questions as possible doing so. It will show dedication towards your development, and will get more people interested in your project.

I like project, but even though you only have one picture, I have a suggestion to be made. I wouldn’t recommend using custom ranks with little custom icons next to the user’s name. It looks ugly and unprofessional. If you’re really trying to recreate the original DeltaScape, which I would very much enjoy, I’d recommend to actually recreate it. They didn’t have any custom ranks - not even donor. Can’t wait to see the progression of this development project, hope to see it prosper.[/quote]

Thank you for the the suggestions, we won’t be using custom ranks they were just in the client from a different project we were making.

The thread was just made in a rush and it will be edited.

Read full topic

item.title: ThetaScape, Re-Creating THE private server with the technology we own today!
item.dc:creator: @Uncalled Uncalled
item.description:
@Uncalled wrote:

I like the development so far. I suggest that you use your thread better, and make it more detailed. Add information regarding the server, what your plans are, if you’re going to be hosting, etc. Just add in filler information and try to kill as many questions as possible doing so. It will show dedication towards your development, and will get more people interested in your project.

I like project, but even though you only have one picture, I have a suggestion to be made. I wouldn’t recommend using custom ranks with little custom icons next to the user’s name. It looks ugly and unprofessional. If you’re really trying to recreate the original DeltaScape, which I would very much enjoy, I’d recommend to actually recreate it. They didn’t have any custom ranks - not even donor. Can’t wait to see the progression of this development project, hope to see it prosper.
